@startuml 时序图-分享梦境
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title 时序图：分享梦境

actor 用户 as User
participant "CommunityController" as Controller
participant "DreamService" as Service
participant "Dream" as Dream
participant "SharedDream" as Shared
database "数据库" as DB

User -> Controller: 选择梦境，点击「分享」，选择匿名/公开
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: shareDream(dreamId, shareType)
activate Service

Service -> DB: 查询梦境
DB --> Service: Dream

alt 梦境已分享
  Service --> Controller: 返回已分享信息
  Controller --> User: 提示已分享
else 未分享
  Service -> Dream: share(shareType)
  activate Dream
  Dream -> Dream: 设置 isShared=true, shareType
  Dream --> Service: 更新后的 Dream
  deactivate Dream

  Service -> Shared: create(dreamId, userId, isAnonymous)
  activate Shared
  Shared -> DB: 插入 SharedDream 记录
  DB --> Shared: 成功
  Shared --> Service: SharedDream
  deactivate Shared

  Service -> DB: 更新 Dream 分享状态
  DB --> Service: 成功

  Service --> Controller: SharedDream
  deactivate Service

  Controller --> User: 分享成功，跳转社区
  deactivate Controller
end

@enduml
